    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this prospective study to try to standardize the care for patients, the investigators are
      planning to compare two cerebral oximeters currently in use at NCH in terms of their accuracy
      in determining the cerebral oxygen saturation as determined by jugular bulb oxygen
      saturation. Also, the investigators will compare these devices in terms of their response to
      changes in hemodynamics that occur during cardiac surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
